_archive/
operational_outputs/

# ASP.NET Core Data Protection key rings — runtime per-host secrets, never source-tracked.
# Each host generates its own keys; committing them across hosts defeats key isolation.
Data/NickFinance.WebApp/dp-keys/
Data/**/dp-keys/
